  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國小粉紅仇日情結深厚，近日中國知名飲用水和飲料公司「農夫山泉」遭波及，起因於中網友悼念中國最大食品飲料生產商「娃哈哈」創辦人宗慶後，大批小粉紅拿娃哈哈與農夫山泉的飲料產品對比，指控農夫山泉包裝疑似包含日本元素，發動出征，導致農夫山泉的股價連日慘跌，讓外界看傻了眼。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzVjYzlkODY0NjUwZDlhYzM4OTUwLmpwZz93aWR0aD01NDAmaGVpZ2h0PTM0OQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/75cc9d864650d9ac38950.jpg?width=540&amp;height=349\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/75cc9d864650d9ac38950.jpg?width=540&amp;height=349\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/75cc9d864650d9ac38950.jpg?width=540&amp;height=349\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n附贈-富含日本元素之  和製漢字 <br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYzg0YjZlOWIwZWU1Y2UzOTNjYTQ5LmpwZz93aWR0aD01MzAmaGVpZ2h0PTQ1Ng\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c84b6e9b0ee5ce393ca49.jpg?width=530&amp;height=456\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c84b6e9b0ee5ce393ca49.jpg?width=530&amp;height=456\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c84b6e9b0ee5ce393ca49.jpg?width=530&amp;height=456\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNmI1NzIxYWRlNTkwMzRjZmRmZjNjLmpwZz93aWR0aD0yODQmaGVpZ2h0PTE3Nw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6b5721ade59034cfdff3c.jpg?width=284&amp;height=177\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6b5721ade59034cfdff3c.jpg?width=284&amp;height=177\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/6b5721ade59034cfdff3c.jpg?width=284&amp;height=177\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
